jroutine-processor 6.0.0

Parallel programming on the go.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
com.github.dm.jrt.processor
Annotation pre-processor classes.
Parallel programming on the go.

Implementation of a Java annotation pre-processor used to generate classes used as proxy of other objects so to support asynchronous calls of the wrapped method.

The generated classes will be based on the jroutine-proxy library, so be sure to include it as a dependency when employing this pre-processor.

Dependencies

Below a full list of the included modules:

  • jroutine-core — core routine and channel classes
  • jroutine-object — routines wrapping object and class methods
